OL,3,CBlack Joy: A new exhibition
OL,4,Ccelebrating Black artists opens in
OL,5,CSussex
OL,7,FWATCH: ITV Meridian's report is by
OL,8,FCharlotte Wilkins.
OL,10,FA new exhibition, launched in Sussex
OL,11,Fis a vibrant celebration of Black Joy!
OL,12,FCurated by Lorna Hamilton-Brown RCA
OL,13,FMBE.
OL,15,FThe thought-provoking exhibition is a
OL,16,Fheartfelt tribute to Black culture,
OL,17,Fresistance and happiness, with joy as
OL,18,Fits central theme.
