OL,3,CBlack Joy: A new exhibition
OL,4,Ccelebrating Black artists opens in
OL,5,CSussex
OL,7,FOne of the artists, Karen Arthur from
OL,8,FSt Leonards, who is founder of a
OL,9,Fmovement called 'Wear Your Happy'
OL,10,Fcreated a stunning gown using recycled
OL,11,Fscaffolding fabric, which she found on
OL,12,Fa building site.
OL,14,FArtists were invited to respond to the
OL,15,Ftheme of Black Joy. In an age where
OL,16,FBlackness is still under attack, the
OL,17,Fidea of Black Joy is an act of radical
OL,18,F(self-)care and an integral part of
OL,19,Fthe ongoing fight for equality.
