OL,3,CBlack Joy: A new exhibition
OL,4,Ccelebrating Black artists opens in
OL,5,CSussex
OL,7,FAs a society, we are facing
OL,8,Foverwhelming challenges and the things
OL,9,Fthat bring us joy and respite should
OL,10,Fbe valued and celebrated.
OL,12,FIllustrator Dorcas Magbadelo says:
OL,14,F"Joy is a good motivator, it's
OL,15,Fsomething we come back to a lot when
OL,16,Fthere's a lot going on in our lives or
OL,17,Faround the world. It's something that
OL,18,Fhelps us to keep going"
